sequenceDiagram
  participant Cron as Cron/Scheduler
  participant Provider as Provider Service
  participant DB as Database
  participant Diff as Incremental Filter
  participant Mail as Mail Service
  participant User as User Inbox

  Cron->>Provider: 1. 定时拉取关键词A/B
  Provider->>DB: 2. upsert 新帖子/视频
  DB-->>Diff: 3. 查找 first_seen_at > 上次任务
  Diff->>Mail: 4. 生成报表内容
  Mail->>User: 5. 发送 HTML 邮件
  User-->>Cron: 6. 下一次任务继续循环
